Dialogue: 10,0:01:11.45,0:01:15.35,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What? No way! What on earth?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:15.35,0:01:20.57,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously! Even though she knows you like Koichi, Misato!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:21.22,0:01:23.44,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What's so good about Koichi anyway?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.65,0:01:26.50,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Misato thinks he's cute.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:27.75,0:01:29.19,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,She does, I'm sure!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:31.57,0:01:33.32,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.32,0:01:35.09,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.09,0:01:36.55,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:36.55,0:01:40.20,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, really? You don't like anyone, Kurumi?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:40.20,0:01:43.05,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But you're so cute! That's such a waste.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:44.69,0:01:46.83,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad I got to become friends with you, Kurumi!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.83,0:01:47.83,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:47.83,0:01:48.71,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:48.71,0:01:50.81,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad we're all friends!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.04,0:01:58.55,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Miyagawa said he liked Kurumi?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.55,0:02:02.83,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,How could he do that? Miki's had a crush on him for so long!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.62,0:02:09.73,Default,Miki,0000,0000,0000,,It's because Kurumi's been exchanging notes with him.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.73,0:02:13.86,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't like it when guys like someone else besides her.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.86,0:02:16.21,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she always does this!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.21,0:02:20.02,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe she calls herself Kurumi when her name is really Ume.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.02,0:02:23.87,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I only became friends with her cause all the guys are \Nwilling to talk to you once you mention her name.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.18,0:02:27.78,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, when Kurumi gets a crush on someone, we'll get in her way, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.78,0:02:29.39,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Since she got in all of ours!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.39,0:02:30.44,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.44,0:02:31.65,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.34,0:02:46.93,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,You're still here.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.26,0:02:50.06,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.77,0:02:52.44,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.90,0:02:54.06,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.06,0:02:56.40,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. Are you staying after for practice?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.67,0:02:58.99,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. Just came to pick something up.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.28,0:03:00.42,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.42,0:03:02.72,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I did leave it here.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.70,0:03:06.70,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.50,0:03:08.21,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.85,0:03:23.09,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really alright?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.97,0:03:35.64,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.75,0:03:39.05,Italics,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,This boy... he was different.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.18,0:03:44.30,Italics,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,This boy, who had so many friends...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.30,0:03:45.34,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the same class again!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.34,0:03:48.21,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,He always saw me as me.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.05,0:03:53.95,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,When I started to like him, I kept my \Nfeelings hidden deep down inside of me.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.53,0:04:03.09,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But I've tried really hard to get him to fall for me too.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.04,0:04:07.23,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I've tried harder at that than I have at school.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.18,0:04:14.44,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I went to Kitahoro high school because he did.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.10,0:04:17.99,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.13,0:04:22.55,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We were in different classes, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.55,0:04:23.60,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.60,0:04:28.21,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I was told to bring this printout to you, class rep!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.21,0:04:29.45,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.45,0:04:32.50,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Don't they look good together?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.19,0:04:36.26,Italics,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I always went to talk to him.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.61,0:04:40.63,Italics,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,So that maybe one day, he'd look at me the same way I look at him.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.40,0:04:43.72,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Practice for the sports festival?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.72,0:04:48.42,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's a drag, but Kazehaya will be \Nthere! Things always seem more fun with him.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.42,0:04:52.53,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! He got elected for sports festival \Nclass rep before he knew what hit him!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.53,0:04:53.02,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.75,0:05:06.53,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I heard that Kazehaya's class D's rep for the sports festival.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.53,0:05:08.07,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.07,0:05:10.88,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should become our class rep, Kurumi!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.05,0:05:13.27,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.27,0:05:16.33,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You totally should!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.33,0:05:19.16,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,This could be your chance, Kurumi!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.16,0:05:23.11,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, it's not like that!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.45,0:05:26.45,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind being class rep though.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.45,0:05:27.59,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Then just do that!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.88,0:05:31.64,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't just elect myself! It's embarrassing!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.18,0:05:36.31,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya! You were picked as a class rep too?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.31,0:05:38.95,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you were too!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.95,0:05:40.09,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.05,0:05:43.19,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,We both got the short stick this time, huh.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.19,0:05:44.89,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,That seat's open.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.89,0:05:46.53,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.83,0:05:51.09,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right, thanks for the CD earlier too.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.09,0:05:55.40,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,No problem. There's actually one I'd like to borrow from you as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.40,0:05:57.25,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. I'll bring it for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.51,0:06:02.25,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,There's been a lot of talk about Sadako lately, hasn't there?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.25,0:06:05.05,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, everyone's gossiping about her.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.44,0:06:08.95,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what kind of girl she really is.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.95,0:06:12.41,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,She's with Kazehaya a lot, isn't she?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.60,0:06:17.43,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, yeah. I wonder if they're dating?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.12,0:06:19.96,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that's not true!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.41,0:06:21.46,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,It could be.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.88,0:06:27.00,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't be that weird for Kazehaya to fall for her, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.20,0:06:32.24,Default,Girls,0000,0000,0000,,It would, it would!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.24,0:06:36.09,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya's just talking to her because he's a nice guy!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.09,0:06:39.16,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,And if he were to fall for someone, it'd definitely be you, Kurumi!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.95,0:06:41.67,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's not possible!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.67,0:06:44.56,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? You two are so close!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.56,0:06:46.96,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,It's just cause we went to the same middle school.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.96,0:06:49.39,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just go out with him?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.39,0:06:50.46,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,We're really not like that!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.46,0:06:54.38,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you don't think so, but what about him?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.23,0:06:59.26,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,You're the reason I do things like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.44,0:07:10.95,Italics,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya was changing right before my very eyes.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.17,0:07:18.46,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, because Sawako pushed herself in between us!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.15,0:07:27.71,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.14,0:07:32.84,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako, you're all sweaty!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.85,0:07:50.27,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.27,0:07:53.74,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it. There, all better.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.46,0:07:57.45,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Did you need something, Kurumi?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.45,0:08:01.44,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no. I just wanted to talk to Sawako.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.03,0:08:04.32,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,We finally got to know each other better recently!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.32,0:08:06.03,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Sawako?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.03,0:08:07.34,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Ri—
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.03,0:08:17.75,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends now, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.35,0:08:23.25,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Lunch time already?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.00,0:08:24.03,Italics,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I need to do something about her.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.69,0:08:27.61,Default,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, lunch time then nap time!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.41,0:08:29.15,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.55,0:08:31.11,Italics,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice. This is the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:35.03,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\t(\fscx95\fscy105)\frz352.771\move(563,494,567,487,26,3904)}I want to thank you. Please meet me \Nbehind the sports equipment room at noon.\NSawako Kuronuma
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.74,0:08:43.00,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,You see?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.00,0:08:45.87,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,We should cheer them on.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.09,0:08:55.95,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya... !
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.56,0:09:06.31,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.85,0:09:09.44,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.20,0:09:21.94,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.41,0:09:29.83,Italics,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Things didn't work out in the end.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.35,0:09:40.69,Italics,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why it couldn't have been me.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.63,0:09:44.99,Italics,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I've always, always liked him.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.51,0:09:48.90,Italics,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I've liked him for much longer than Sawako has.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.73,0:09:52.01,Italics,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.23,0:10:04.79,Italics,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what would've happened if I'd \Nconfessed to him before he met Sawako?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.07,0:10:11.71,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm being stupid!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.59,0:10:16.67,Italics,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I did my best, it was just impossible.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.67,0:10:18.89,Italics,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,It was Kazehaya's decision, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.66,0:10:30.35,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya and I wouldn't make a good couple, would we?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.48,0:10:34.64,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not true—
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.64,0:10:37.28,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Then I want you to support us.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.64,0:10:42.20,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one I've told about this.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.66,0:10:47.66,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you think there's someone better for him.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.05,0:10:52.36,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,No. I think you two would make a great couple.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.36,0:10:54.50,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako! Then you'll—
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.50,0:11:02.62,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't. I wouldn't be able to fully \Nsupport you from the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.73,0:11:07.54,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya's special to me too.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.71,0:11:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I can't agree.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.84,0:11:20.89,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I can't help you, but I understand how you feel!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.89,0:11:23.23,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,So at least I could listen to you if—
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.23,0:11:24.68,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,How annoying.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.80,0:11:31.39,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Why isn't she backing off?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.95,0:11:37.21,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Can't she feel the difference between us?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.83,0:11:41.05,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,That voice is coming from Kurumi's direction.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.00,0:11:44.55,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Is there someone else there behind her?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.98,0:11:47.82,Italics,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako's a lucky girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.82,0:11:50.37,Italics,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,But it's just so strange.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.41,0:11:52.87,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.60,0:11:58.82,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me Kurumi anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.18,0:12:03.30,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,U-Ume?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.71,0:12:07.96,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.96,0:12:15.51,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Your name is going into my book of People Who've Called Me Ume.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:12.00,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz23.687\frx32\fry2\pos(536,250)}People Who've \N Called Me Ume
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.51,0:12:20.59,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako Kuronuma!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.92,0:12:25.11,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay if I call you that?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.11,0:12:27.55,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.98,0:12:29.95,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.05,0:12:32.39,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Ume, wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.78,0:12:34.10,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me Ume!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.12,0:12:36.81,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, then what should I call you?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.35,0:12:45.53,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Ume is the only thing I hate about myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.17,0:12:52.04,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't group yourself in with me.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.04,0:12:55.42,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know anything about me.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.85,0:13:02.31,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I've liked Kazehaya since middle school.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.65,0:13:08.82,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I've tried so hard to talk to him, to \Nmake sure he didn't get a girlfriend...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.82,0:13:12.85,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You've worked so hard...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.85,0:13:15.32,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.77,0:13:21.37,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway. I know him better than anyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.93,0:13:24.94,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't some two day crush.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.94,0:13:26.19,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I've always liked him!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.19,0:13:28.00,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been waiting for him.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.58,0:13:34.76,Italics,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako always faces everything and everyone straight on.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.42,0:13:38.79,Italics,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,She faces me, and Kazehaya, the same way.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.45,0:13:42.65,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, you're annoying!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.65,0:13:46.59,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't worked for him at all! Why do \Nyou deserve to be around him all the time?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.59,0:13:48.01,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.01,0:13:51.50,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I thought if it were you my competition, \Nthere was no way I could lose!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.30,0:14:01.78,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I like him so, so much more than you do.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.76,0:14:04.63,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I do!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.51,0:14:23.75,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're much cuter the way you are \Nnow than you were when I first met you.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.23,0:14:26.60,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I know I'm cute!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.20,0:14:31.73,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.51,0:14:36.41,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,If Kazehaya doesn't think so, what does it matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.30,0:14:44.64,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I know he doesn't like me.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.36,0:14:48.86,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I know because I've always been watching him.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.12,0:14:53.65,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come back?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.65,0:14:59.05,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to see me like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.64,0:15:08.16,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Because you know him so well.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.62,0:15:14.80,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Because I thought we could understand each other.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.65,0:15:22.95,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.10,0:15:35.06,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,She's so dense.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.07,0:15:42.11,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, do you think that Kazehaya possibly likes me?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.45,0:15:48.45,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Me? Who was friendless until recently?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.60,0:15:53.72,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya doesn't judge people like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.98,0:16:03.19,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,He's nice and always wants to help people.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.43,0:16:07.36,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,He always gives people the benefit of the doubt.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.07,0:16:12.73,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,When he laughs, you can't help but \Nfeel better and laugh along with him.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.73,0:16:16.05,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! And he's serious when it matters.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.17,0:16:21.13,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,He actually has a quick temper, but it's \Nbecause he cares about doing the right thing!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.13,0:16:23.78,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,He's nice to both guys and girls.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.77,0:16:24.84,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,He's honest,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.84,0:16:26.41,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,and—
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.99,0:16:29.01,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I talking to you about this?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.30,0:16:34.90,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy we were able to talk like this. \NI've never spoken like this to anyone before.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.30,0:16:37.00,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,This was my best shot.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.00,0:16:38.64,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,We just entered high school together.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.81,0:16:45.77,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,People were finally supportive of us.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.53,0:16:49.71,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,If I wanted to make him like me, it was now or never!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.93,0:16:53.30,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yet...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.82,0:16:56.19,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over now.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.49,0:17:00.85,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya thinks I like Arapin.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.53,0:17:06.31,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what I say now, it'll just look \Nlike I'm denying it out of embarrassment!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.39,0:17:10.49,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I had planned on giving up at that point.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.17,0:17:12.66,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,But then Sawako said..
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.15,0:17:14.90,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,That's no good.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.13,0:17:22.14,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't like it when Kazehaya accidentally thought I liked Sanada.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.46,0:17:26.10,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,But since it's a misunderstanding, \Nhe'll understand if you talk to him.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.31,0:17:32.57,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think he'd really understand if I told him the truth?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.51,0:17:35.37,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.47,0:17:47.39,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.00,0:17:48.62,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Kaze—
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.34,0:17:53.46,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.58,0:17:58.62,Italics,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want him to... misunderstand me!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.35,0:18:00.94,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.89,0:18:03.10,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Kazehaya!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.35,0:18:07.31,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like Pin!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.71,0:18:14.45,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I like you, Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.08,0:18:19.21,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I've always, always liked you, Kazehaya!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.36,0:18:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.64,0:18:29.24,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,It's always been you.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.50,0:18:31.78,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't possibly like anyone else.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.29,0:18:41.20,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Kurumizawa.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.20,0:18:41.96,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.40,0:18:44.60,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,It was my fault.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.00,0:18:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.51,0:18:56.13,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,But I have someone I like.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.21,0:19:02.30,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I like her more than anyone else.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.15,0:19:05.17,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.37,0:19:11.21,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I know. It's so obvious.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.20,0:19:18.76,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,But did my confession make you feel happy at all? Even just a little?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.07,0:19:22.65,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it did.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.72,0:19:24.65,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.96,0:19:39.96,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Will you call me by my name? Just once?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.06,0:19:43.85,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Ume.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.49,0:19:54.26,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,That typical old woman's name isn't that bad after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.26,0:19:59.13,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to tell you at all, but \NI guess not everything goes as planned.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.13,0:20:00.30,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,As planned?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.05,0:20:04.56,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,You have no taste in women, Kazehaya!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.52,0:20:06.64,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.32,0:20:12.78,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I told him.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.27,0:20:23.70,Italics,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't like me at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.17,0:20:29.37,Italics,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,But ever since then,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.90,0:20:33.29,Italics,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't had to use the book of People Who've Called Me Ume.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.42,0:20:37.60,Italics,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he'll accept them from me.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.35,0:20:44.02,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako will definitely make chocolates herself.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.26,0:20:55.49,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Ayane and Chizu probably won't.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.30,0:21:04.07,Italics,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow's the last time.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.54,0:21:13.88,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going with the expensive one!
