Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.81,0:21:58.16,Ed - E,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\blur3}I like you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.41,0:22:04.59,Ed - R,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\blur3}kimi ga suki de
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.41,0:22:04.59,Ed - E,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\blur3}I've always liked you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.30,0:22:10.97,Ed - R,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\blur3}kono omoi koi demo ii
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.30,0:22:10.97,Ed - E,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\blur3}I don't mind if this emotion is what they call love,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.04,0:22:14.29,Ed - R,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\blur3}kizu tsuitemo ii
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.04,0:22:14.29,Ed - E,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\blur3}and I don't care if I get hurt by it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.66,0:22:19.13,Ed - R,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\blur3}nando demo tsutaetai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.66,0:22:19.13,Ed - E,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\blur3}I just want to tell you, over and over again
