Dialogue: 10,0:22:25.91,0:22:27.02,Preview Dialog,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I want to give them to him.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:27.61,0:22:28.82,Preview Dialog,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:29.62,0:22:31.13,Preview Dialog,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop hesitating.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:31.72,0:22:33.97,Preview Dialog,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Valentine's Day.
